::SnowCat::

She walked around the entrance of the ARK.  She kept looking up at 
the sky.  She missed her snow covered mountains and hunting in the 
snow. It was what her beast mode did best. She wished she could run 
and play in the snow. Like she did when she first arrived to this 
planet.  She layed down on the entrance ramp and rested her ehad on 
her large paws.  She sighed and thought about her snow covered 
mountains.
